name: cs740-final-project
description: This project measures DNS resolution time and full page load time across resolver profiles: - **public_udp**: Public resolvers over UDP (8.8.8.8, 1.1.1.1) - **isp_udp**: ISP resolver over UDP - **dot**: DNS-over-TLS (via Stubby) - **doh**: DNS-over-HTTPS (via cloudflared)
